Source code for the paper
-------------------------

Samuel Gerber, Peer-Timo Bremer, Valerio Pascucci, Ross Whitaker
"Visual Exploration of High Dimensional Scalar Functions"
IEEE Transactions on Visualization and Computer Graphics to appear, Proceedings of VIS 2010


To compile HDViz and HDVizProcessing you will need the following libraries:

blas
lapack
gfortran
opengl
glut
freetype

for HDVizImagePCA you additioanlly need ITK.


Compiling is easiest with CMAKE using the inlcuded CMakeLists.txt file.
